  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 60ca56eaf6709b64596738cfd9ce6584, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueSystem
  narrationCanvas: {fileID: 412797125517151513}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 5230433253337963604}
  portraitImage: {fileID: 2234135905177987396}
  anim: {fileID: 0}
  sentences:
  - oh,hello there
  - well,ist your first time here isnt it?
  - down worry let me teach you how its done here
  - My name is Roland, I'm one of the agents of LobotomyCorp, your new workplace
  - Specifically, the cleaning department where we are in charge of...
  - tearing apart faculties infested with anomalies
  - You know, if you don't take good care of your head, you could get distorted and
    become one of those things.
  - Roland....
  - Angelica???
  - Are you bothering the newbie?....huh..explain the basic mechanics to him and
    leave him alone, got it?
  - Yes Madam...
  - First things first, to face the anomalies we depend on our E.G.O equipment.
  - These are processed anomalies turned into weapons; these weapons can be problematic
    because they feed on emotions.
  - As I told you, if you don't take care of your mind you can go crazy, which is
    understood as becoming distorted.
  - People who, after experiencing traumatic events, are consumed by their emotions
    and influenced by anomalies
  - In short, the advantage of our E.G.O. equipment is that we can use its power
    to our advantage.
  - 'These are classified into 4 levels of power and danger: Zahyin, Teth, He, and
    Waw; the greater the power, the greater the risk of distortion.'
  - Not to brag, but I own one of the Teth class
  - Well, even though Angelica has a "Waw" category...which means we don't overlap
    much at work...
  - Well, when using your E.G.O. Equipment, you'll have an emotion meter when you
    hit or take damage, and also when you're stagger.
  - Huh? What's stagger? It's when you take a lot of damage that damages your equipment.
  - This causes you pain and mental collapse that blocks your basic functions This
    causes you pain and mental collapse that blocks your basic functions
  - In short, you're Fuck
  - Okay, rookie, that's all. Practice the movement for your first mission; you don't
    want to die at the hands of those things.
